metadata.name: Selfie with the Whale Shark
metadata.description:
An amazing  experience in Olsob Cebu, Philippines. 

Weekend getaway with my girlfriend turned my wifey üòç

This is one memorable trip wherein we woke up as early as 5am to swim with this beauty. The thing though while swimming with them, the fishermen gotta continuously feed them with baby shrimps so they stay close to us. Turned out I had some of the baby shrimps, upset my stomach and I ended up staying in a washroom to flash it for almost the rest of the day.

End of story, we manage to still go on a date late night before ending our day üòç
